LB Victorias Secrets comparable sales including direct sales declined 5 but sales at comparable stores only were down 7 And it could get much much worse according to Jefferies analyst Randal Konik who has an Underperform rating on the stock and a price target of 16 Konik has been ringing the alarm on the segments Pink brand in particular which posted comparable sales declines in the low doubledigits he wrote in a note published Wednesday night The combination of Victorias Secrets sales decline Pinks underwhelming sales and more discounting means the brands are unraveling Konik wrote We see earnings continuing to spiral lower over the next two years which is counterconsensus he said Clearly these comments are alarming especially because the stock is 1214 quickly Be careful I dont get a good felling here Im worried
